ent搜索哪家强？人大高瓴&amp;快手联合发布全新评测基准GISA</span></a></span></p>\n       <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38425925925925924\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: auto;max-width: 100%;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 8px;border-top-right-radius: 8px;border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(153, 153, 153, 0.3) 2px 4px 8px 0px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100021713\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=928977b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5gibgibpTuuwBnUMazyfFpnLT1WBd1miagy6wSBtDfSl2olFDYTibicEKmVbwvIrjJ5LUKlia71AwQY9k4vnfkj5NkRtqY60AxHbgpeKRHicwL1DF4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n       </figure>\n       <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文题目：《Immersion&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">in</span></spa