\"font-weight:bold;float:unset;background-color:unset;box-shadow:none;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;text-shadow:none;background-position-y:0%;border-top-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);border-top-left-radius:0px;overflow-x:unset;overflow-y:unset;background-image:none;height:auto;text-align:left;border-right-width:1px;line-height:1.8em;border-right-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);border-top-right-radius:0px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;border-bottom-width:1px;background-origin:padding-box;padding-right:0px;border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:1px;border-bottom-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;border-left-color:rgb(145, 109, 213);font-size:18px;margin-left:0px;transform:none;flex-direction:unset;text-indent:0em;border-left-style:solid;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;margin-top:0px;padding-top:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;padding-bottom:0px;border-left-width:5px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-style:none;justify-content:unset;align-items:unset;margin-bottom:0px;-webkit-box-reflect:unset;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心优势：为何“真实” SWE 数据至关重要？</span></span></h2>\n       <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:8px;letter-spacing:0.02em;padding-left:0px;font-size:14px;padding-bottom:8px;line-height:1.8em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，为了追求数据的规模化（Scaling），业界经常依赖自动化流程生成合成数据（例如 SWE-smith 和 SWE-Mirror）。尽管这种方式能够基于少量仓库迅速产出数以万计的数据，但分析指出，</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);font-weight: bold;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: left;background-position-y: top;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;